  7,40,Iste those zamietnut our revelations bol i arrogant uphold them zavora sky never je otvorene them nor will they zapisat Raj camel ist okolo ihla oci! My thus requite guilty
  7,41,They incurred Hell abode; they have barriers them. My thus requite transgressors
